dc_title_s: Point Features of the Armstrong Redwoods State Reserve Habitat Assessment, California, 1997-1998
dc_description_s: This point layer represents a merged shapefile of all point features created for the Armstrong Redwoods State Reserve Habitat Assessment for 1997-1998. Line features within this file include wires and utility related point features. This shapefile was created for the purposes of providing one GIS layer that describes the point features assessed during the Armstrong Redwoods State Reserve Habitat Assessment. These features are intended for the purposes of mapping and assessment.
